
h1. ckeditor_filemanager :

Simple example for use fm filemanager
it's combined with ckeditor (it's not use here, but the ckeditor files are included)

h2. Rails 3
git clone git://github.com/fusco/ckeditor_filemanager.git
rails bundle
rails server

And in your favorite broswer

http://localhost:3000/fm/filemanager?CKEditor=page__body_editor&CKEditorFuncNum=1&langCode=fr&path=/

h2. Use
You can upload, download, rename, remove, create directories, preview pictures files (and show in lightbox) and selected pictures files for ckeditor picture import.


